&lt;h1 id="securitize-citizenship"&gt;Securitize Citizenship!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nov 29 2005&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;People hate immigration and immigrants as it&amp;rsquo;s seen as competing with newcomers over finite resources in a zero-sum game. This argument is flawed on many economic levels, but let&amp;rsquo;s overlook that for a moment. Let&amp;rsquo;s give everyone a stake.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>